I thought you were a dick and a snob who watches only those oscar bait dumb movies which are liked by "professional movie critics". But now that i saw this video I'm gonna subscribe to you cos you were brave enough to tell us how you actually feel about these underrated and controversial movies.

Some people just can't like these movies cps they are too dumb to find the deep messages hidden in the movie. Like the part where KJ fell in love with the bear even when they are completely different and flawed. Really deep stuff but some people can't see that SMH.

Well i think i said all i needed to. I hope your video gets more people to actually say what they feel about these great movies. You just got a new fan and i will check more of your videos. I also can't wait for the 4th film!!!!
